                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px; background: #e8f4fd; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 13px; color: #2c3e50;">
                <strong>📊 Summary:</strong> 3 recruiters from Barcelona area with verified emails and LinkedIn profiles.
                All are from well-known tech/finance/retail companies.
            </div>
